    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine. This unit boasts a meticulously maintained high-pressure VANOS system and crisp individual throttle bodies, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis integrity is absolute, with zero subframe fatigue and a suspension setup that remains tight and responsive, preserving its original kinematics. Finished in pristine original paint with an interior devoid of bolster wear, this vehicle is a mechanically superior example of BMW\u2019s high-revving naturally aspirated era. Turn-key and ready for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
