    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like factory finish, devoid of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of bolster wear, while the dashboard and trim pieces are entirely free of sun damage or scratches. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a complete, documented service history and recent preventative maintenance. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
