    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of superlative caliber, preserved in impeccable, showroom-original condition. This specimen exhibits an unblemished exterior finish paired with a cabin that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and mechanically flawless, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class, catering to the most exacting automotive standards. An investment-grade opportunity for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
