    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor \u2013 absolutely pristine inside and out! I've babied this car since day one, and it really shows. No scratches, no weird smells, just pure driving bliss. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner so incredibly happy. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
