    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a peerless example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and remains in factory-spec internal health, with a recently serviced VANOS system and rod bearings. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a factory-fresh suspension geometry. Finished in collector-grade condition with zero deferred maintenance, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal performance.",
